No. 10-74. Javier Rivera Aquino, Secretary, Puerto Rico Department of Agriculture, et al., Petitioners v. Suiza Dairy, Inc., et al. 563 U.S. 1001, 131 S. Ct. 2441,

179 L. Ed. 2d 1235,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 3604. May 16, 2011.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the First Circuit denied.

Justice Kennedy took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 587 F.3d 464.
